text: Issy-les-Moulineaux () is a commune in the southwestern suburban area of Paris, France, lying on the left bank of the river Seine. It is one of Paris' entrances and is located from Notre-Dame Church. The city welcomes headquarters of major companies such as Coca-Cola France, Microsoft France, France 24, Jet Solidaire, Sodexo. == References == ==Other websites== * Issy City Hall * Issy Tourism Office * Issy TV Category:Communes in Hauts-de-Seine
